When installing vmtools, when installing multiple times, segment Fault will also appear when using the default options
sudo ./vmware-install.pl --d 
You can see from the above picture
If it keeps popping up, it will affect something
我在不同的虚拟机 20.04 21.04... 会报这样的错误
